long _kg
: kg		_kg ! ;
: kg@		_kg @ ;
: lb		100000 220462 */ kg ;	\ 2.20462 lb/kg
long _cm
: cm		_cm ! ;
: cm@		_cm @ ;
: in		254 100 */ _cm +! ;	\ 2.54cm/in
: ft		0 cm 12 * in ;

\ general scaling and rounding --- 1234567 100 /ROUND . --- 12346
: /ROUND ( n mod -- n2 )	SWAP OVER U/MOD SWAP ROT 2/ => IF 1+ THEN ;

\ BMI = kg/(m*) BMI is weight in kilograms divided by height in meters squared
: BMI		kg@ cm@ DUP * 10000000 SWAP */ 100 /ROUND ;

: .HEALTH
	BMI 185 < IF ." Underweight" EXIT THEN
	BMI 250 < IF ." Healthy" EXIT THEN
	BMI 300 < IF ." Overweight" EXIT THEN
	." Class " 'I' BMI 250 - 50 / EMITS ."  obesity"
;
: .GOAL ( bmi -- )

\ If over then suggest max weight for healthy etc.  BMI = kg/(m*)

: .SUGGESTION
	BMI 185 < IF 185 .GOAL THEN
	BMI 249 > IF 249 .GOAL THEN
;
: .BMI		BMI .AS" *|.# is " .HEALTH .SUGGESTION ;

local realBoard = {}	-- true/false = mine/no mine
local myBoard = {}		-- x = mine / 0-8 = surrounding mine count
local gameState = {}	-- 0 = undiscovered / 1 = discovered / 2 = flag / 3 = ?

-- settings:
local width = 9		-- board width
local height = 9		-- board height
local density = 0.123	-- avg mines/tile (nil to ignore) [0.123 = beginner / 0.156 = intermediate / 0.206 = expert]
local mines = 10		-- mine count
if density then mines = width*height*density end
local deterministic = false	-- avoid 50/50 guess cases (currently unimplemented)
local openFirstMove = true	-- ensure first move lands on a tile with 0 surrounding mines

--[[	default board settings:
    beginner : 9x9/10
	intermediate : 16x16/40
	expert : 30x16/99
--]]

local function shuffle(table)
	local buffer
	for i = #table, 1, -1 do
		local r = math.random(1,i)
		buffer = table[i]
		table[i] = table[r]
		table[r] = buffer
	end
end

local function isValid(x, y)
	return x>0 and x<=width and y>0 and y<=height
end

local function getNeighbors(i)	-- gets neighbor indexes
	local neighbors = {}
	local x = (i-1)%width + 1
	local y = math.floor((i-1)/width)+1
	
	for ix = x-1, x+1 do
		for iy = y-1, y+1 do
			if isValid(ix, iy) then
				table.insert(neighbors, ix+(iy-1)*width)
			end
		end
	end
	
	return neighbors
end

local function countNearbyMines(i)
    local total = 0
    for _, i in ipairs(getNeighbors(i)) do
        if realBoard[i] then total += 1 end
    end
    return total
end

local function labelTiles()
	for i, bomb in ipairs(realBoard) do
		if not bomb then return end
		for _, n in ipairs(getNeighbors(i)) do
			if not realBoard[n] then
				myBoard[n] = myBoard[n]+1
			else
				myBoard[n] = "X"
			end
		end
	end
end

local function getGameState()	-- 0 = in progress / -1 = lost / 1 = won
    local win = true
	for i, v in ipairs(realBoard) do
        if v and gameState[i] == 1 then
            return -1
        end
        if win and not v and gameState[i] ~= 1 then
            win = false
        end
    end
    if win then return 1 end
    return 0
end

local function win()	-- does stuff when you win
end

local function lose()	-- does stuff when you lost
end

local function update()
    -- add visual updates to the board here
    local state = getGameState()
    if state == -1 then return lose() end
    if state == 1 then return win() end
end

local function open(x,y)
    local i = x+(y-1)*width
    if not isValid(x, y) then return end
    if not gameState[i] == 0 then return end
    gameState[i] = 1
    update()
end

local function cord(x,y)
    local nearbyFlags = 0
    for _, i in ipairs(getNeighbors(x+(y-1)*width)) do
        if gameState[i] == 2 then
            nearbyFlags += 1
        end
    end

                open(ix,iy)
            end
        end
    end

end

local function flag(x,y)
end

local function buildBoard()	-- creates physical game board
end

local function setupBoard()
	realBoard = {}
	myBoard = {}
    gameState = {}
	
	mines = clamp(mines, 1, width*height-1)
	for i = 1, width*height do
        gameState[i] = 0
		myBoard[i] = 0
		realBoard[i] = false
		if i <= mines then
			realBoard[i] = true

title: Backup and restore partitions
content:
action

# Подсчет количества разделов на накопителе /dev/sda
partitions=$(lsblk -n -o NAME -r /dev/sda | wc -l)

# Создание резервной копии GPT таблицы накопителя с помощью gdisk
gdisk /dev/sda -b ./gpt_bak.bin

# Сохранение каждого раздела накопителя в отдельный файл сжатый с помощью lzma
for ((i=1; i<=$partitions; i++)); do
    part_file="part_${i}.img.lzma"
    dd if=/dev/sda${i} bs=4M | lzma -9 -T4 > $part_file
done


counteraction

# Восстановление таблицы разделов из резервной копии
gdisk /dev/sda < ./gpt_bak.bin

# Восстановление каждого раздела
for ((i=1; i<=$partitions; i++)); do
    part_file="part_${i}.img.lzma"
    lzma -d -c $part_file | dd of=/dev/sda${i} bs=4M
done

#!/usr/bin/env python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
#
#  método place
#
# Script que implementa un formulario de inscripción a cursos
#

import tkinter as tk
from tkinter import ttk
from tkinter import messagebox
from pprint import pprint


def guardar():
	global alumnos
	
	# leo los datos
	
	nombre = caja_nombre.get()
	if nombre.isspace() or not nombre:
		messagebox.showerror(title="ERROR", message="Nombre inválido")
		return 1
	
	
	edad = caja_edad.get()
	if not edad.isdecimal() or int(edad) <= 0 or int(edad) > 100:
		messagebox.showerror(title="ERROR", message="Edad incorrecta")
		return 1
	
	
	dni = caja_dni.get()
	if not dni.isdecimal() or int(dni) <= 0 or int(dni) > 100_000_000:
		messagebox.showerror(title="ERROR", message="DNI inválido")
		return 1
	
	
	
	email = caja_email.get()
	if not "@" in email:
		messagebox.showerror(title="ERROR", message="Email inválido")
		return 1
	
	curso = lista_cursos.get()
	if not curso:
		messagebox.showerror(title="ERROR", message="Seleccione un curso")
		return 1
	
	aceptacion = estado.get()
	if not aceptacion:
		messagebox.showwarning(title="Advertencia", message="Debe aceptar los términos y condiciones")
		return 1

	
	
	# guardo los datos
	alumno = {
		"nombre": nombre,
		"edad": edad,
		"dni": dni,
		"email": email,
		"curso": curso
	}
	alumnos.append(alumno)
	
	# muestro los datos
	print()
	pprint(alumnos)
	
	# borro el formulario
	caja_nombre.delete(0,tk.END)
	caja_email.delete(0,tk.END)
	caja_dni.delete(0,tk.END)
	caja_edad.delete(0,tk.END)
	estado.set("False")



# Datos: una lista de diccionarios (cada dicc es un alumno)
alumnos = [] 


############# Parte gráfica ####################

# creo la ventana de mi formulario
form = tk.Tk()
form.title("Formulario de inscripción")
form.config(width=400, height=400)

# evito que mi formulario sea redimensionable
form.resizable(False,False)


# campo nombre
label = ttk.Label(text="Nombre")
label.place(x=20, y=20)
caja_nombre = ttk.Entry()
caja_nombre.place(x=120, y=20, width=250, height=25)


# campo edad
label = ttk.Label(text="Edad")
label.place(x=20, y=70)
caja_edad = ttk.Entry()
caja_edad.place(x=120, y=70, width=250, height=25)


# campo dni
label = ttk.Label(text="Dni")
label.place(x=20, y=120)
caja_dni = ttk.Entry()
caja_dni.place(x=120, y=120, width=250, height=25)


# campo email
label = ttk.Label(text="Email")
label.place(x=20, y=170)
caja_email = ttk.Entry()
caja_email.place(x=120, y=170, width=250, height=25)


# campo cursos
label = ttk.Label(text="Cursos")
label.place(x=20, y=220)
lista_cursos = ttk.Combobox(
					state = 'readonly',
					values = ["C++", "Java", "Python", "JavaScript", "HTML"]
			)
lista_cursos.place(x=120, y=220, width=250, height=25)


# casilla de verificación
estado = tk.BooleanVar()
estado.set("False")
casilla = ttk.Checkbutton(text="Acepto términos y condiciones",variable=estado)
casilla.place(x=80, y=270)

# boton
boton = ttk.Button(text="Guardar", command=guardar)
boton.place(x=140, y=320, width=120, height=40)









form.mainloop()

--lua
-- Last Update 31/08/2023
-- TO Ver.5936 // ADDED Revive, Spot Farm, Goto Spot 

local RestHP = 35    -- Porcentagem para quando descansar HP - Percentage for when to rest HP
local RestMana = 35  -- Porcentagem para quando descansar MANA - Percentage for when to rest MANA
local Ataque1 = 1  --skill a usar - skill to use
local Ataque2 = 2  --skill a usar - skill to use
local Ataque3 = 3 --skill a usar - skill to use
local Ataque4 = 2 --skill a usar - skill to use
local Ataque5 = 2 --skill a usar - skill to use
local HealPet = 6 -- skill Heal Pet - skill Heal Pet
local HealPetEvery = 5 -- Heal Pet a cada ( EX: 5 Mobs ) - Heal Pet every (EX: 5 Mobs)
local UseBuff = 7 -- Skill Buff - Skill Buff
local UseBuffEvery = 30 -- Usa Buff a cada ( EX: 30 Mobs ) - Uses Buff every (EX: 30 Mobs)
local PetAtaque = "e" -- skill Heal Pet
local PotionHP = 5   -- ( "x" para sentar), ( 8 ou outro para atalho potion) - ("x" to sit), ( 8 or other for potion shortcut)
local PotionMana = 6 -- ( "x" para sentar), ( 9 ou outro para atalho potion) - ( "x" to sit), ( 9 or other for potion shortcut)

-- Ir ao local de farm - Go to farm location
local Map = "m" -- Atalho mapa - Shortcut map
local SpotFarm = {358, 432}  -- Lugar onde vai clicar no mapa - Place where you will click on the map
local JackStrawOK = {566, 310} -- Posicao OK para usar jackstraw - Position OK to use jackstraw
local OKButton = {516, 469} -- Posicao do OK, reviver sem jackstraw - Position of OK, revive without jackstraw



log("")

local Mob = 0
local Heal = 0
local Buff = 0
local Unst = 0

-- Client base address
local CLIENT = 0x00400000


-- ponteiros HP Char Health xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
-- HP
local HP_POINTER = readmem(CLIENT + 0x00C12980, "d")
function getHp()
    return readmem(HP_POINTER + 0x320, "d")
end
 --xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx final ponteiros HP Char Health xxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
 
 -- MAX HP
local p_MaxHP = readmem (CLIENT + 0x00C12980, "D")

-- HP PLUS
local p_HPPlus = readmem (CLIENT + 0x00C12980, "D")
function HpPlus()
    local plus = readmem(p_HPPlus + 0x3EC, "b") % 100
    return plus > 0 and plus or 1
end
 
-- BUFF HP
local p_Buff = readmem (CLIENT + 0x00C12980, "D")
function GetBuff()
    return readmem (p_Buff + 0x3E8, "D")
end

-- Mana buff
local MANA_BUFF_POINTER = readmem(CLIENT + 0x00C12980, "d")
function getManaBuff()
    return readmem(MANA_BUFF_POINTER + 0x2B8, "d")
end

-- Mana
local MANA_POINTER = readmem(CLIENT + 0x00C12980, "d")
-- Returns your current mana value 
function getMana()
    return readmem(MANA_POINTER + 0x324, "d")
end

-- Max mana
local MAX_MANA_POINTER = readmem(CLIENT + 0x00C12980, "d")
function getMaxMana()
    return readmem(MAX_MANA_POINTER + 0x2B4, "d") + getManaBuff()
end
--xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx final ponteiros Mana Char xxxxxxxxx

-- ponteiros HP Mob xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
local pointer_15 = readmem (0x00400000 + 0x00EBFAF8, "D")
local pointer_16 = readmem (pointer_15 + 0x18, "D")
local pointer_17 = readmem (pointer_16 + 0xEA4, "D")
local pointer_18 = readmem (pointer_17 + 0x0, "D")
local pointer_19 = readmem (pointer_18 + 0xC, "D")
local pointer_20 = readmem (pointer_19 + 0x43C, "D")
local target_HP = readmem (pointer_20 + 0x8, "D")

-- xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

-- ponteiros Char Name xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
local charNameOffsets = {0x30, 0x0, 0x44, 0x18}
local CHAR_NAME_POINTER = readmem(CLIENT + 0x00D369DC, "d")
for i = 1, #charNameOffsets 
do
    CHAR_NAME_POINTER = 
        readmem(CHAR_NAME_POINTER + charNameOffsets[i], "d")
end

function getCharName()
    local name = readmem(CHAR_NAME_POINTER + 0x408, "s", 30)
    
    -- If name is alphanumeric return it safely
    if string.match(name, "^[%w]+$") then return name
    else 
        -- Else read it with offset
        return readmem(readmem(CHAR_NAME_POINTER + 0x408, "d") + 0x0, "s", 30)
    end
end
MyCharName = getCharName()
log("<<< "..MyCharName.." is Starting... >>>")
-- xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

::RESET::
log ("<<< Reseting Values % >>>")
-- HP e MP MAXIMO ANTES DE INICIAR O BOT - PRECISA ESTAR CHEIO
-- HP MAXIMO
function MaxiHP()
    local hp = readmem(p_MaxHP + 0x3E4, "d") + GetBuff()
    local pluses = HpPlus()

    if pluses == 1 then return hp
        else return math.floor(((hp * pluses) / 100) + hp)
    end
end

local MaximumHP = MaxiHP()
local MaximumMana = getMaxMana()

-- X position
local xOffsets = {0x30, 0x0, 0x44, 0x40}
local X_POINTER = readmem(CLIENT + 0x00D369DC, "d")
for i = 1, #xOffsets
do
    X_POINTER = readmem(X_POINTER + xOffsets[i], "d")
end

-- Y position
local yOffsets = {0x30, 0x0, 0x44, 0x40}
local Y_POINTER = readmem(CLIENT + 0x00D369DC, "d")
for i = 1, #yOffsets
do
    Y_POINTER = readmem(Y_POINTER + yOffsets[i], "d")
end

-- Returns char's x-axis location
function getX()
    local x = readmem(X_POINTER + 0x7BC, "f") / 20
    return x > 0 and math.floor(x) or math.ceil(x)
end

-- Returns char's y-axis location
function getY()
    local y = readmem(Y_POINTER + 0x7C0, "f") / 20
    return y > 0 and math.floor(y) or math.ceil(y)
end

while true do -- LOOP 1
    count = 2

-- CALCULO % HP
local Health = getHp()
local CurrentHP = tonumber(Health)
local MaxHP = tonumber(MaximumHP)
HPPercentage = (CurrentHP / MaxHP) * 100

-- CALCULO % MP
local Mana = getMana()
local CurrentMana = tonumber(Mana)
local MaxMana = tonumber(MaximumMana)
local ManaPercentage = (CurrentMana / MaxMana) * 100

-- CONFERE SE PORCENTAGEM E MAIOR QUE 100% E VAI RESETAR
if HPPercentage > 100 then
    goto RESET
    end
	
function waitUntilFarmSpot()
    local countspot = 0 -- Inicializa a contagem
    local prevX, prevY -- Variaveis para armazenar as coordenadas anteriores
    while true do
        local x = getX()
        local y = getY()
        --log(x, y)
        if prevX == x and prevY == y then -- Verifica se a coordenada atual é a mesma da anterior
            countspot = countspot + 1 -- Incrementa a contagem
            if countspot >= 3 then -- Verifica se a contagem é maior ou igual a 3
                log("Ready to start again !!! ")
                break -- Interrompe o loop
            end
        else
            countspot = 0 -- Reseta a contagem se a coordenada mudar
        end
        prevX, prevY = x, y -- Atualiza as coordenadas anteriores
        wait(1000) -- wait for 1 second before checking again
    end
end

function GotoSpot()
	send (Map)
	local Condition = "a"
	if Condition ~= nil then
    for i = 1, #Condition
    do
    right(SpotFarm[1] + 20, SpotFarm[2] + 20) -- clica com offset para resetar o ponto
	wait(500)
	right(SpotFarm[1], SpotFarm[2])
	wait(500)
	send (Map)
    waitUntilFarmSpot()
    FARM()
    end
    end
end

-- Check char is dead
function DEAD()
	local ConditionB = "b"
	local hpJ = getHp() 
	if hpJ < 1 then
	wait("1s") 
	log("Char "..MyCharName, "is Dead !")
	wait("1s") 
	if ConditionB ~= nil then
		for i = 1, #ConditionB
		do
		log("Trying to use Jackstraw")
		left(JackStrawOK[1], JackStrawOK[2])
		left(JackStrawOK[1], JackStrawOK[2]) wait("3s")
		end
		end
        local hpn = getHp() 
		if hpn < 1 then
			log("Jackstraw not found, Reviving normal...")
            left(OKButton[1], OKButton[2])
			left(OKButton[1], OKButton[2]) wait("3s")
            end
        log("Char "..MyCharName, "is Live Again !")
        SIT()
		log("Sitting to recover HP")
        send(PotionHP) wait("17s") 
		send(PotionHP) wait("17s") 
		send(PotionHP) wait("17s") 		
        log("Char "..MyCharName, "is Returning to Battle !")
		GotoSpot()	
	end
end

function SIT()
    send("ESC", 200)
    wait("2s") -- ESPERA DA LEAVE BATTLE
    send(PotionHP, 50) -- ATALHO PARA POTION HP
    end

function SITMP()
    send("ESC", 200)
    wait("2s") -- ESPERA DA LEAVE BATTLE
    send(PotionMana, 50) -- ATALHO PARA POTION HP
    end

function COUNT()
    if count > 1 then
        Mob = Mob + 1
        Heal = Heal + 1
        Buff = Buff + 1
        log("")
        log("Bot Name: "..MyCharName)
        log("HP = "..string.format("%.2f", HPPercentage).."%") -- PRINT HP %
        log("Mana = "..string.format("%.2f", ManaPercentage).."%") -- PRINT MANA %
        log("Mobs Killed!: " .. Mob)
        log("Count to Buff: " .. Buff)
        log("Count to Heal Pet: " ..Heal)
        count = 1
        end
        end

function HEALPET()
    if Heal == HealPetEvery then
        log("<<<<< Healing Pet >>>>>")
        send(HealPet, 200)
        Heal = 0
        end
        end

function USEBUFF()
    if Buff == UseBuffEvery then
        wait("1s")
        log("<<<<< Using Buff >>>>>")
        send (UseBuff, 500)
        Buff = 0
        end
        end

function RECOVER()
    if HPPercentage < RestHP then
        wait(200)
	if readmem (target_HP + 0x02DD8, "D") > 3 then -- SE TIVER MOB ATACANDO
        while readmem (target_HP + 0x02DD8, "D") > 3 do
        send(Ataque1, 200)
        send(Ataque2, 200)
        send(Ataque3, 200)
        send(Ataque4, 200)
        send(Ataque5, 200)
        UNSTUCK()
        DEAD()
    end
    SIT()
        else
            SIT()
            while getHp() < MaximumHP do
                if readmem (target_HP + 0x02DD8, "D") > 3 then -- SE TIVER MOB ATACANDO
                while readmem (target_HP + 0x02DD8, "D") > 3 do
                send(Ataque1, 200)
                send(Ataque2, 200)
                send(Ataque3, 200)
                send(Ataque4, 200)
                send(Ataque5, 200)
                UNSTUCK()
                DEAD()
            end
            SIT()
                else
                wait("1s")
                end
                Unst = 0
                end
                end
                end

    if ManaPercentage < RestMana then
    if readmem (target_HP + 0x02DD8, "D") > 1 then -- SE TIVER MOB ATACANDO
    while readmem (target_HP + 0x02DD8, "D") > 1 do
        send(Ataque1, 200)
        send(Ataque2, 200)
        send(Ataque3, 200)
        send(Ataque4, 200)
        send(Ataque5, 200)
        UNSTUCK()
        DEAD()
    end
    SIT()
        else
            SITMP()
            while getMana() < MaximumMana do -- CORRIGIDO ERRO DE ESPERAR MANA ENCHER
                if readmem (target_HP + 0x02DD8, "D") > 1 then -- SE TIVER MOB ATACANDO
                while readmem (target_HP + 0x02DD8, "D") > 1 do
                    send(Ataque1, 200)
                    send(Ataque2, 200)
                    send(Ataque3, 200)
                    send(Ataque4, 200)
                    send(Ataque5, 200)
                    UNSTUCK()
                    DEAD()
                end
                SITMP()
                else
                wait("1s")
                end
                Unst = 0
                end
                end
                end
				end

function TAB()
    send("tab", 100)
    --log("Sending Tab!")
    end

function PETATK()
    send(PetAtaque, 50)
    end

function UNSTUCK()
    Unst = Unst + 1
    currentMP = getMaxMana()
    currentMobValue = readmem (target_HP + 0x02DD8, "D")
    if (currentMP == MaximumMana) and (Unst > 20) then
        log("<<<<< Trying to Unstuck! >>>>>")
        Unst = 0
        FARM()
    end
    if Unst > 1000 then
        Unst = 0
        end
        end


function ATK()
while readmem (target_HP + 0x02DD8, "D") > 1 do
    send(Ataque1, 200)
    send(Ataque2, 200)
    send(Ataque3, 200)
    send(Ataque4, 200)
    send(Ataque5, 200)
    UNSTUCK()
    DEAD()
    end
    end

function FARM()
::TAB::
    TAB()
    if readmem (target_HP + 0x02DD8, "D") > 500 then
        log("Target Found!")
        elseif readmem (target_HP + 0x02DD8, "D") < 1 then
           --log("Target not Found! Searching...")
           goto TAB
        end
    PETATK()
    ATK()
    COUNT()
    HEALPET()
    USEBUFF()
    RECOVER()
    end


FARM()
end -- FINAL LOOP 1

import pyautogui
import keyboard
import textwrap

# This variable will store the coordinates of the sunduk after Ctrl+C is pressed
sunduk = None  

def capture_coordinates(): 
    global sunduk
    # Store the current mouse position in the sunduk variable
    sunduk = pyautogui.position()  
    print(sunduk)

def move_to_sunduk():
   # Check if sunduk coordinates have been captured
   if sunduk is not None: 
       current_position = pyautogui.position()
       # Mouse down to start dragging  
       pyautogui.mouseDown()
       # Drag mouse to sunduk coordinates
       pyautogui.dragTo(sunduk)  
       # Mouse up to finish dragging
       pyautogui.mouseUp()
       # Move mouse back to original position
       pyautogui.moveTo(current_position)
       print(current_position)

# Bind Ctrl+C to capture sunduk coordinates  
keyboard.add_hotkey('ctrl+c', capture_coordinates)

# Bind Ctrl+X to move mouse to sunduk
keyboard.add_hotkey('ctrl+x', move_to_sunduk)

def print_instructions():
   instructions = """To use: Press Ctrl+C to capture coordinates of chest. 
   Then press Ctrl+X to drag&drop selected item to sunduk. 
   (Note: selected item don't need to be clicked).
    The script works correctly for transferring items
    from the car to the chest.
   """
   
   print(textwrap.fill(instructions))

print_instructions()
keyboard.wait('esc')
